	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you do not have something with better stats in your range slot by the time you are big enough to get one of these then you better re-evaluate your gear. As for the effect: It would not suck as a prok. The little bits of extra damage always help. It also wouldn't suck it the casting time was 2-3. I got one of these and always found better things to do in the 7 seconds this would take to cast. I ended up destroying mine within minutes, so I never got to see the graphics people say look so cool. Maybe it does look really cool. I'm not here to dog on its looks, only its uselessness.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
