	   <tr><td colspan=2>Got one off a crystal spiderLING last night in Crystal Caverns.<br><br>Effect is Velium Shards, Zero Range, 7 second cast, 12 hit points maximum damage.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>Can't be used for pulling, do more melee damage in 7 seconds H2H as a monk.<br><br>It DOES have +1 to all resists, so this is a useful item for some magic runs.  Other than that, this is a toy.  It looks cute when equipped.  It makes spell effects.<br><br>Zinj, Fat Monk of Norrath<br>47th Rung on the Ladder of Life, Vazaelle.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
